Hi,

We are working on it, via one of these libraries:
- https://github.com/marsender/cops
- https://github.com/marsender/silex-cops

But the job is not finished yet !

Hi,

Thanks for this links.
I also don't like Calibre dependency...
In fact, cops and silex-cops don't use calibre itself but only calibre database.
So I use my own script "epub-loader" https://github.com/marsender/cops/tree/master/resources/epub-loader to parse epup directory and generate a Calibre database on the fly.

OPDS support is now ready.
Here is the url: http://atoll-digital-library.org/opds/
